CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper September 25, 1943, pg. unknown, reads: "Joe Johns and His Boxing Troupe Visit Bedridden Soldiers at Veterans Hospital - On his way to Camp Shenango last Monday, Sgt. Joe Louis and his touring troupe of boxers stopped off at the Veteran's hospital in Butler to visit some of the inmates...  Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Boxer Joe Louis and other army or military men in yard of Shenango or Butler Veterans' Hospital, with veterans in bathrobes
